Generate a single command to apply all code changes. Use the exact file paths provided in the previous steps. Create a command using 'cat' with heredocs for each file, assuming execution from the repository root. Format:

(cat << 'EOF' > "frontend/src/components/Example.js"
// File content
EOF
cat << 'EOF' > "frontend/src/components/AnotherFile.js"
// File content
EOF
)

Ensure correct handling of spaces in file paths. Output only the command, no explanations.
